Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.64,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}那隻白鳥
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.42,0:22:46.75,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在天空中翱翔
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.75,0:22:51.83,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}天際間有誰在呼喚著我
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.95,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}不用擔心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.95,0:23:06.80,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}要事我始終銘記
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.80,0:23:10.66,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}萬千思緒
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.96,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}此時湧上心頭
